snippet: The half brother of a former leader of the island nation appears to have been elected president, ending a tumultuous process.
abstract: Abdulla Yameen, half brother of former President Maumoon Abdul Gayoom, appears to have won presidential runoff election in Maldives.
lead_paragraph: The half brother of a former leader of the island nation appears to have been elected president, ending a tumultuous process.

headline.main: Runoff Vote Is Completed in Maldives
headline.print_headline: Runoff Vote Is Completed In Maldives
